O:a) "\\(Q \\cap (Q - R)\\)", b) "\\(Q - (Q \\cup R)\\)", c) "\\(Q - (Q \\cap R)\\)", d) "\\(Q \\cup (Q - R)\\)"
R:"Set difference \\(Q-R\\) removes elements in \\(R\\) from \\(Q\\). This is equivalent to removing the intersection: \\(Q - (Q \\cap R)\\)."
}

q {
